439 static void DPC_ObjDet_quadFit(float *x, float*y, float *xv, float *yv)
440 {
441  float a, b, c, denom;
442  float x0 = x[0];
443  float x1 = x[1];
444  float x2 = x[2];
445  float y0 = y[0];
446  float y1 = y[1];
447  float y2 = y[2];
448 
449  denom = (x0 - x1)*(x0 - x2)*(x1 - x2);
450  a = (x2 * (y1 - y0) + x1 * (y0 - y2) + x0 * (y2 - y1)) / denom;
451  b = (x2*x2 * (y0 - y1) + x1*x1 * (y2 - y0) + x0*x0 * (y1 - y2)) / denom;
452  c = (x1 * x2 * (x1 - x2) * y0 + x2 * x0 * (x2 - x0) * y1 + x0 * x1 * (x0 - x1) * y2) / denom;
453 
454  *xv = -b/(2*a);
455  *yv = c - b*b/(4*a);
456 }

475 static void DPC_ObjDet_rangeBiasRxChPhaseMeasure
476 (
477  DPC_ObjectDetection_StaticCfg *staticCfg,
478  float targetDistance,
479  float searchWinSize,
480  uint16_t *detMatrix,
481  uint32_t *symbolMatrix,
482  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *compRxChanCfg
483 )
484 {
485  cmplx16ImRe_t rxSym[SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
486  cmplx16ImRe_t *tempPtr;
487  float sumSqr;
488  uint32_t * rxSymPtr = (uint32_t * ) rxSym;
489  float xMagSq[SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
490  int32_t iMax;
491  float xMagSqMin;
492  float scal;
493  float truePosition;
494  int32_t truePositionIndex;
495  float y[3];
496  float x[3];
497  int32_t halfWinSize ;
498  float estPeakPos;
499  float estPeakVal;
500  int32_t i, ind;
501  int32_t txIdx, rxIdx;
502 
503  uint32_t numRxAntennas = staticCfg->ADCBufData.dataProperty.numRxAntennas;
504  uint32_t numTxAntennas = staticCfg->numTxAntennas;
505  uint32_t numRangeBins = staticCfg->numRangeBins;
506  uint32_t numDopplerChirps = staticCfg->numDopplerChirps;
507  uint32_t numSymPerTxAnt = numDopplerChirps * numRxAntennas * numRangeBins;
508  uint32_t symbolMatrixIndx;
509 
510  uint16_t maxVal = 0;
511 
512  truePosition = targetDistance / staticCfg->rangeStep;
513  truePositionIndex = (int32_t) (truePosition + 0.5);
514 
515  halfWinSize = (int32_t) (0.5 * searchWinSize / staticCfg->rangeStep + 0.5);
516 
517  /**** Range calibration ****/
518  iMax = truePositionIndex;
519  for (i = truePositionIndex - halfWinSize; i <= truePositionIndex + halfWinSize; i++)
520  {
521  if (detMatrix[i * staticCfg->numDopplerBins] > maxVal)
522  {
523  maxVal = detMatrix[i * staticCfg->numDopplerBins];
524  iMax = i;
525  }
526  }
527 
528  /* Fine estimate of the peak position using quadratic fit */
529  ind = 0;
530  for (i = iMax-1; i <= iMax+1; i++)
531  {
532  sumSqr = 0.0;
533  for (txIdx=0; txIdx < numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
534  {
535  for (rxIdx=0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
536  {
537  symbolMatrixIndx = txIdx * numSymPerTxAnt + rxIdx * numRangeBins + i;
538  tempPtr = (cmplx16ImRe_t *) &symbolMatrix[symbolMatrixIndx];
539  sumSqr += (float) tempPtr->real * (float) tempPtr->real +
540  (float) tempPtr->imag * (float) tempPtr->imag;
541  }
542  }
543 #ifdef SUBSYS_DSS
544  y[ind] = sqrtsp(sumSqr);
545 #else
546  y[ind] = sqrt(sumSqr);
547 #endif
548  x[ind] = (float)i;
549  ind++;
550  }
551  DPC_ObjDet_quadFit(x, y, &estPeakPos, &estPeakVal);
552  compRxChanCfg->rangeBias = (estPeakPos - truePosition) * staticCfg->rangeStep;
553 
554  /*** Calculate Rx channel phase/gain compensation coefficients ***/
555  for (txIdx = 0; txIdx < numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
556  {
557  for (rxIdx = 0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
558  {
559  i = txIdx * numRxAntennas + rxIdx;
560  symbolMatrixIndx = txIdx * numSymPerTxAnt + rxIdx * numRangeBins + iMax;
561  rxSymPtr[i] = symbolMatrix[symbolMatrixIndx];
562  xMagSq[i] = (float) rxSym[i].real * (float) rxSym[i].real +
563  (float) rxSym[i].imag * (float) rxSym[i].imag;
564  }
565  }
566  xMagSqMin = xMagSq[0];
567  for (i = 1; i < staticCfg->numVirtualAntennas; i++)
568  {
569  if (xMagSq[i] < xMagSqMin)
570  {
571  xMagSqMin = xMagSq[i];
572  }
573  }
574 
575  for (txIdx=0; txIdx < staticCfg->numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
576  {
577  for (rxIdx=0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
578  {
579  int32_t temp;
580  i = txIdx * numRxAntennas + rxIdx;
581  scal = 32768./ xMagSq[i] * sqrt(xMagSqMin);
582 
583  temp = (int32_t) MATHUTILS_ROUND_FLOAT(scal * rxSym[i].real);
584  MATHUTILS_SATURATE16(temp);
585  compRxChanCfg->rxChPhaseComp[staticCfg->txAntOrder[txIdx] * numRxAntennas +
586  rxIdx].real = (int16_t) (temp);
587 
588  temp = (int32_t) MATHUTILS_ROUND_FLOAT(-scal * rxSym[i].imag);
589  MATHUTILS_SATURATE16(temp);
590  compRxChanCfg->rxChPhaseComp[staticCfg->txAntOrder[txIdx] * numRxAntennas
591  + rxIdx].imag = (int16_t) (temp);
592  }
593  }
594 }

693 {

695

699  {

704  winType = DPC_DPU_DOPPLERPROC_FFT_WINDOW_TYPE;
705  }

707  mathUtils_genWindow((uint32_t *)cfg->hwRes.hwaCfg.window,
708  cfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps,
709  DPC_ObjDet_GetDopplerWinGenLen(cfg),
710  winType,
711  DPC_OBJDET_QFORMAT_DOPPLER_FFT);

713  return(winType);

730 static void DPC_ObjDet_GetRxChPhaseComp(DPC_ObjectDetection_StaticCfg *staticCfg,

783 int32_t DPC_ObjectDetection_execute
784 (
785  DPM_DPCHandle handle,
786  DPM_Buffer* ptrResult
787 )
788 {
789  ObjDetObj *objDetObj;
790  SubFrameObj *subFrmObj;
791  DPU_RangeProcHWA_OutParams outRangeProc;
792  DPU_StaticClutterProc_OutParams outStaticClutter;
793  DPU_DopplerProcHWA_OutParams outDopplerProc;
794  DPU_CFARCAProcHWA_OutParams outCfarcaProc;
795  DPU_AoAProcHWA_OutParams outAoaProc;
796  int32_t retVal;
797  DPC_ObjectDetection_ExecuteResult *result;
798  DPC_ObjectDetection_ProcessCallBackCfg *processCallBack;
799  int32_t i;
800 
801  objDetObj = (ObjDetObj *) handle;
802  DebugP_assert (objDetObj != NULL);
803  DebugP_assert (ptrResult != NULL);
804 
805  DebugP_log1("ObjDet DPC: Processing sub-frame %d\n", objDetObj->subFrameIndx);
806 
807  processCallBack = &objDetObj->processCallBackCfg;
808 
809  if (processCallBack->processFrameBeginCallBackFxn != NULL)
810  {
811  (*processCallBack->processFrameBeginCallBackFxn)(objDetObj->subFrameIndx);
812  }
813 
814  result = &objDetObj->executeResult;
815 
816  subFrmObj = &objDetObj->subFrameObj[objDetObj->subFrameIndx];
817 
818  retVal = DPU_RangeProcHWA_process(subFrmObj->dpuRangeObj, &outRangeProc);
819  if (retVal != 0)
820  {
821  goto exit;
822  }
823  DebugP_assert(outRangeProc.endOfChirp == true);
824 
825  if (processCallBack->processInterFrameBeginCallBackFxn != NULL)
826  {
827  (*processCallBack->processInterFrameBeginCallBackFxn)(objDetObj->subFrameIndx);
828  }
829 
830  objDetObj->stats.interFrameStartTimeStamp = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
831 
832  DebugP_log0("ObjDet DPC: Range Proc Done\n");
833 
834  if (subFrmObj->dynCfg.staticClutterRemovalCfg.enabled == 1)
835  {
836  retVal = DPU_StaticClutterProc_process(subFrmObj->dpuStaticClutterObj,
837  &outStaticClutter);
838 
839  if (retVal != 0)
840  {
841  goto exit;
842  }
843  }
844 
845  retVal = DPU_DopplerProcHWA_process(subFrmObj->dpuDopplerObj, &outDopplerProc);
846  if (retVal != 0)
847  {
848  goto exit;
849  }
850 
851  /* Procedure for range bias measurement and Rx channels gain/phase offset measurement */
852  if(objDetObj->commonCfg.measureRxChannelBiasCfg.enabled)
